criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — explicitly defined the project scope, inputs (initial investment, revenues, costs, tax, terminal value) and hurdle rate;  
Implement — documented storing data and running code ("define and store this data" / "we wrote this code");  
Validate — computed NPV, IRR, payback and scenario NPVs;  
Evolve — ran sensitivity scenarios (20% revenue drop, WACC variations);  
Reflect — drew explicit conclusions about drivers of value (terminal value, revenue sensitivity) and recommended risk mitigation.
